trans-unit.source: Specifies the code-beside handler information in the <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.IWorkflowDebugger.BeforeHandlerInvoked(System.Guid,System.Guid,System.String,System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.ActivityHandlerDescriptor)" /> and <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.IWorkflowDebugger.UpdateHandlerMethodsForActivity(System.Guid,System.Guid,System.String,System.Collections.Generic.List{System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.ActivityHandlerDescriptor})" /> methods.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.IWorkflowDebugger.BeforeHandlerInvoked(System.Guid,System.Guid,System.String,System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.ActivityHandlerDescriptor)" /> 및 <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.IWorkflowDebugger.UpdateHandlerMethodsForActivity(System.Guid,System.Guid,System.String,System.Collections.Generic.List{System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.ActivityHandlerDescriptor})" /> 메서드의 코드 병행 처리기 정보를 지정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> representing the name of the handler method.
The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> representing the CLR metadata token identifier for the handler method.
trans-unit.target: 처리기 메서드의 CLR 메타데이터 토큰 식별자를 나타내는 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" />입니다.
